                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Found 2 new static analysis issues in 2.7.62-15-g3c39aeb:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Pointer may be dereferenced after it was positively checked for NULL&lt;/b&gt;
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;tt&gt;lustre/osd-ldiskfs/osd_compat.c&lt;/tt&gt;: in &lt;em&gt;osd_obj_update_entry&lt;/em&gt;, Pointer &apos;oi&amp;#95;fid&apos; checked for NULL at line 581 may be dereferenced at line 589.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Null pointer may be dereferenced&lt;/b&gt;
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;tt&gt;lustre/osd-ldiskfs/osd_compat.c&lt;/tt&gt;: in &lt;em&gt;osd_obj_update_entry&lt;/em&gt;, Null pointer &apos;oi&amp;#95;fid&apos; that comes from line 570 may be dereferenced at line 589.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;


